I still miss Gumby! 😃

snippet.textDisplay:
Season 9 Coke Studio​ was fantastic. So many awesome songs.
On Top of the list would be
1: Paar Chana dae by Ali Hamza and Shilpa Rao 
2: Rung by Amjad Sabri (Late) and Rahat Fateh Ali Khan 
3: Aaqa by Abida Parveen and Ali Sethi
4: Shaman paey gaiyan , ki dam da paroosaa by Rachel Vicajee
5: Mann Kunto Maula by Javed Bashir and Ali Azmat​
6: Tu kuja man kuja
7: Afreen Afreen
8: Nawazishen Karam by Momina and Asim 
9: Uddi Jaa
10:Lagi Bina-Chal Mele Noon Challiye By Saieen Zahoor and Sanam Marvi,
